d/Bad Breeding merits from the Ventrue clanbook are not available for use at this time.%0a> %0a> *Banned Bloodlines are the following: Bohagande, Norvegi%0a> %0a90c109,113%0a%3c %0a---%0a> [[#Tijuana]]%0a> [++'''Tijuana origins for PC's'''++]%0a> %0a> Tijuana is currently at war with San Diego. You may have a character sired by an NPC in Tijuana and you have escaped the brutal regime there. Keep in mind, Tijuana vampires are largely antagonists, your sire may make an appearance (and could make a good story). There are, however, no Carthians or Ordo Dracul in Tijuana.%0a> %0a100a124%0a> [[http://www.wantonwicked.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=250&t=32374|General iXP]]%0a
